README file for PROFFIT v1.4, a software for the extraction of X-ray surface-brightness profiles.

If you find this software useful, please don't forget to cite Eckert et al. 2011, A&A 526, 79 in your publications.

********* INSTALL *******************

To install PROFFIT, you must first have a version of the ROOT data analysis framework (>=5.24, see http://root.cern.ch/drupal/content/downloading-root) and of the CFITSIO and WCS libraries. Binary distributions are sufficient in both cases. See the PROFFIT user guide for more information:

http://www.isdc.unige.ch/~deckert/proffit_guide.html

To install the software (for C shell variants):

Untar the software package and define the PROFFIT directory:

tar xvf proffit_1.5_cmake.tar.gz
cd proffit_1.5/
make


